==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: free-for-all
<hw>free-for-all</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a noisy and
disordered fight conducted without rules.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> brawl.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>Any vigorous competition in
which anyone can compete, with few or no rules, and in which the winner
is unpredictable; <as>as, when they began to distribute the free food,
the orderly line of hungry recipients degenerated into a
<ex>free-for-all</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Free-hand</ent>⟦br⟧
